# Packaged theme directories live here too (one per omarchy theme variant).
# They're built by scripts/package-themes.py in the Wallpapers repo and
# uploaded to Hetzner by scripts/sync-hetzner.sh, so don't commit them.
# Only the site files (index.html, sw.js, build-site.sh, wallpapers.json,
# .github/, fonts/) need to be in git.
/*/
